
Folders:

feeds
Contains getnews.py, the driver script that should be run to classify and categorize news from various feeds after build models to classify and categorize.

classify
Contains the instructions in README file to generate the model to classify news items relevant to BHRRC (tagged with  '__label__HR__') and news items that are not relevant to BHRRC (tagged with '__label__NON_HR__').

categorize
Contains the instructions in README file to generate 2 models: model to categorize a news item at middle levels and a model to categorize a news item at leaf levels.

util
contains utility functions used by python code in other 3 directories.
